---
import Layout from "@layouts/root.astro";
---

<Layout page="Cookie Policy" description="How Veblex uses cookies and similar technologies across our services.">
    <main class="flex-1">
        <article
            class="mx-auto container max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16"
        >
            <section>
                <a
                    href="/legal"
                    class="text-muted-foreground font-mono uppercase underline-offset-2 transition-all duration-300 hover:underline"
                >
                    Legal
                </a>
                <h1 class="my-4 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
                    Cookie Policy
                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
                    How Veblex uses cookies and similar technologies.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">
                    Last updated: April 12, 2026
                </p>
            </section>

            <section id="what-are-cookies" class="mt-12">
                <h2 class="text-xl">What Are Cookies</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 text-muted-foreground">Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit Veblex services. They help us remember preferences, analyze usage, and deliver a seamless experience across the ecosystem.</p>
            </section>

            <section id="essential-cookies" class="mt-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl">Essential Cookies</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 text-muted-foreground">These cookies are necessary for Veblex services to function properly, including authentication via Veblex Auth, session management, and security features.</p>
            </section>

            <section id="analytics-cookies" class="mt-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl">Analytics Cookies</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 text-muted-foreground">We use analytics cookies to understand how users interact with Veblex services. This data helps us improve performance and user experience across all products.</p>
            </section>

            <section id="preference-cookies" class="mt-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl">Preference Cookies</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 text-muted-foreground">These cookies remember your settings and choices — such as language, theme, and layout preferences — so you don't have to reconfigure them on each visit.</p>
            </section>

            <section id="managing-cookies" class="mt-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl">Managing Cookies</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 text-muted-foreground">You can control cookies through your browser settings. Note that disabling certain cookies may affect the functionality of Veblex services.</p>
            </section>

            <section id="contact" class="mt-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl">Contact</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 text-muted-foreground">For questions about our cookie practices, contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@veblex.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-2">legal@veblex.com</a>.</p>
            </section>
        </article>
    </main>
</Layout>
